room_title: Escape room "The Mummy's Curse" by Mystery Room Houston in Houston
room_description:
Your team was assigned to investigate the mysterious disappearance of the archeological team assigned to find the golden bust of the Pharaoh. When you step into the tomb, the door traps you inside. You have 60 minutes to solve the secrets of the pyramids before the Mummy returns...
Note: Groups of 10 and more players will start in separate rooms and join together later in the scenario.
